T1  - Can News Be a Major Source of Aggregate Fluctuations? A Bayesian DSGE Approach
AU  - FUJIWARA, IPPEI
AU  - HIROSE, YASUO
AU  - SHINTANI, MOTOTSUGU
Y1  - 2011/02/01
